# Crypto Trading Indicator — environment configuration
#
# To enable LunarCrush social intelligence (Galaxy Score, AltRank, sentiment):
#   1. Subscribe to a plan at https://lunarcrush.com  (then open Settings -> API)
#   2. Copy this file to ".env"  (same folder as app.py)
#   3. Paste your key after the "=" below
#   4. Restart the app
#
# The .env file is read automatically on startup. Keep it private — it is a
# credential. The app works fine without it; LunarCrush panels just stay off.

LUNARCRUSH_API_KEY=
